h government contracts; 35 qubits.",GNS:"AI education platform; low float with aggressive move history.",BLDP:"Hydrogen fuel cell leader; green policy tailwinds accelerating.",DVLT:"Meme coin airdrop with set dates; active Robinhood feeds.",BTBT:"Bitcoin miner pivoting to AI compute; dual BTC + AI narrative.",BBGI:"Former runner spiked to $16.69 from $3.70; crowd memory."};
